nodes.text: Per your suggestion, I decided to get real. So here is the real Phyllis. I never said that you had to support anything. And voting for the democratic party does not prove that one likes democracy. And I never said that you had to support George Bush, nor did I say you had to be a republican. This is the real Phyllis signing off.
Well, either the real or imaginary Phyllis implied those things in the post under discussion.
